🎶 AI-Powered Lyrics Generator 🎶
This project is a dynamic lyrics generator that creates song lyrics based on user-provided themes or emotions. Whether you're a songwriter, poet, or just someone who loves music, this tool helps you craft meaningful lyrics effortlessly!

✨ Features:
✔️ AI-Generated Lyrics – Get custom song lines based on your input.
✔️ Beautiful UI – A sleek and interactive design for a smooth experience.
✔️ Instant Results – Generates lyrics in seconds with a simple click.
✔️ Personalized Touch – Every lyric includes e/kashi55 and Under25, making it unique!

🛠️ Tech Stack Used:
🔹 Flask (Python) – Backend framework for processing lyric generation.
🔹 HTML, CSS, JavaScript – For the interactive and aesthetic web page.
🔹 Jinja2 (Flask Templates) – For rendering dynamic content.
🔹 Prompt Engineering (AI-Assisted) – Used AI-powered prompts to enhance lyric generation.

💡 Inspiration & Purpose:
Created by Kashish Valecha, this project is for music lovers who feel the rhythm of words. It blends creativity and technology, making songwriting effortless and fun!

🎤 Ready to craft your next masterpiece? Try it out now! 🎶🔥
